@node Story "What is Moria 3D about"

              Moria 3D

You, the hero, are bored by youre unintresting life, so you set out
to conquer Moria to find the lost rings of old. Before you can descent
a level deeper into Moria you will have to find a number of rings or
other items.

 @{"<< README                 " link "README/main"}
