@endnode

@node Requirements "What you need to run Moria 3D"

@{b}Required:@{ub}

  · MC68030 or better
  · AGA or some graphics card
  · It will run on a MC68000 if you recompile but who likes Slideshows?

@{b}Recomended:@{ub}

  · MC68040+ CPU
  · Some sort of graphics card

@{b}Compatibility:@{ub}

To insure maximum compatibility Moria3D has been tested on many systems
including but not limited to:

  · Eagle 4000TE / Cyberstorm 060      / CGFX V3 / 48 MB Fast (my system)
  · A4000T       / Apollo 060          / P96     / 32 MB Fast
  · Draco 060                          / CGFX V3 / 16 MB
  · A4000        / 040                 / AGA     /  8 MB Fast
  · A1200        / Blizzard 030-50+FPU / AGA     /  4 MB Fast
  · AROS         / Linux P120                    / 32 MB
  · PowerUp -at work-

So far no compatibility problems have been reported
     and no crashes or hangs appeared.

