@node Installing "How to install Moria 3D"

Installing Moria 3D is fairly simmple.

Just Pickup the Moria3D drawer and drag it anywhere you like.

There is nothing more to be done.

 @{"<< Requirements           " link Requirements}
 @{">> How to run Moria 3D    " link Running}

@endnode

@node Running "How to run Moria 3D"

Just look for the icon appropriate to youre system in the Moria3D drawer.

On a 68020 and 68030 you start Moria.020.exe
On a 68040 and 68060 you start Moria.040.exe

@{b}DON´T TRY TO START Moria.040.exe ON 68020 and 68030 IT WILL JUST CRASH. @{ub}

On a 68040 and 68060 Moria.020.exe will still work but the 68040 is faster on
those systems.

 @{"<< Installing Moria 3D    " link Installing}
