@node Moveing "How do I move?"

Most movements are done using the mouse.

The left mouse button moves forward and the right button moves backward.
The position of the mousepointer turns the player. Mousepointer at top
turns upwards and so on.

Further movemnts are done by using 7 to turn anticlockwise and 9 to turn clockwise.

By pressing <ESC> you can quit the Game.

Aditional Keys:

´l´ and ´L´ change Light levels. ´+´ and ´-´ change the position of the viepoint.
Play around with these to see how they work. If you thing you made a mess quit the
game and everything will be back to normal again.

